<br>
Most of the items out there that already have haste or other such effect probably don't need to be tampered with, for the simple reasoning that those items stay in use even when compared against some of the most uber items in the game right now.  <br>
<br>
The changes would only work if they encompassed every class in the proposed changes, and gave each class a say so in what kind of focuses would benefit them.  <br>
<br>
Very good thoughts though :-)  Someone should possibly send this idea to Sony and see if any results come up.  The epics, while Kunark era, are still one of the hardest tests for each of the classes.  Some of them are more difficult than others, even to the point of no one even wanting to bother getting their epic.   <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=222062">Booperbustle Tinkermeister</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
